	<text xml:lang="de">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott mitt uns, fuͤrgeliepter sun, ich danck <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p477" cert="high">dir</persName> und <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20082" cert="high">Susanna</persName> umb die hürlig; hab ich nächt mitt unserm volck geässen.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de">In dinem embieten und fuͤrnemmen bestäte dich gott; der sye din hilff,</foreign> et festina, quantum potes, ut res tuas in tutum componas; sic etiam me levabis onere gravissimo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Was ich hab, schicken ich dir hie.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Der <persName type="auto_name">pfaltzgraff von Craca</persName> schribt mir, köndt nitt früntlicher, uß <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l853" cert="high">Poland</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aliquando videbis.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Unser <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p527">Joannes</persName> ligt kranck zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Craka</placeName>; wirt bald me bottschafft kummen.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Me kan ich diser zyt nitt schryben.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott mitt üch allen.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">30. iunii in yl yl 1570.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullinger</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Minem lieben sun <persName ref="p477" cert="high">Hansen Rodolffen Bullingern</persName>, pfarreren zuͦ <placeName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="l35">Berg</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
